<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1366973" src="https://i0.wp.com/www.bellanaija.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/75223574_166573781097063_6616023485774928100_n.jpg?resize=1080%2C1080&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="1080" height="1080" data-recalc-dims="1" /> GQ South Africa is celebrating their first-ever ‘Man of the Year’ awards with three spectacular covers, featuring men who have shaped the cultural landscape, and have been the most intelligent and inspirational people of the year. The award was held in partnership with Hennessy on Sunday night at The Houghton Hotel, with the aim of celebrating people who have made a significant impression in their various fields of expertise. The event was also about celebrating GQ’s 20 years in South Africa. Check out the covers and the winners of the events: <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1366990" src="https://i2.wp.com/www.bellanaija.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/74600064_152622482668651_8057407163434239960_n.jpg?resize=1080%2C1350&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="1080" height="1350" data-recalc-dims="1" /> Actor John Kani looking dapper is one of three cover stars and a recipient of the GQ Men of the Year Lifetime Achievement Award. He features alongside singer Nasty C and designer Tristan Du Plessis, who was among the winners at the inaugural GQ Men of the Year Awards ceremony. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1366991" src="https://i0.wp.com/www.bellanaija.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/75294319_430658334283635_6397562521592357843_n.jpg?resize=1080%2C1350&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="1080" height="1350" data-recalc-dims="1" /> Other champions on the night include the likes of Siya Kolisi, Vusi Themebkwayo, Thembinkosi Lorch, and Lady Skollie. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1366989" src="https://i2.wp.com/www.bellanaija.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/75534229_605495793525735_5044546917640810307_n.jpg?resize=1080%2C1350&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="1080" height="1350" data-recalc-dims="1" /> Check out 